{"id":232844348,"title":"家暴該忍嗎？","content":"我有兩個小孩還小3歲跟1歲。但我長期被言語羞辱及槌身體、打巴掌對待。這是我第二次逃離那個地方。距離上次是一年半前，我已經為了小孩忍了下來。腦裡ㄧ直有個小孩在單親家庭長大這樣真的很可憐。但我真的不想回去過那種日子！我該繼續為了小孩忍下去嗎？","excerpt":"我有兩個小孩還小3歲跟1歲。但我長期被言語羞辱及槌身體、打巴掌對待。這是我第二次逃離那個地方。距離上次是一年半前，我已經為了小孩忍了下來。腦裡ㄧ直有個小孩在單親家庭長大這樣真的很可憐。但我真的不想回去","anonymousSchool":true,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f11e8d02-6756-4376-9db3-e1cca4d2a66c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-07T12:23:04.636Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-07T12:23:04.636Z","commentCount":26,"likeCount":23,"tags":["HIDE_THUMBNAIL"],"topics":["家暴"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"結婚","forumAlias":"marriage","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":23}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[],"postAvatar":""}